{"tid":965382,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"古天樂得選最喜愛男歌手完全冇問題","createTime":"2019-01-02T04:05:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T05:24:44.000Z","uid":62609,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5c2931e283f14d73ff71fa63c1356c347bfedbe7","tid":965382,"uid":62609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T04:05:15.000Z","msg":"好多人成日拉埋投建制派黎講，其實完全兩回事<br />\n<br />\n如果有個最受歡迎區議員候選人係比左建制派我覺得冇問題，因為單純係講人氣，佢地蛇餅糭齋實有人氣<br />\n<br />\n但投選區議員係要講能力，睇佢係咪真係幫到區內人，所以建制當選我會屌<br />\n<br />\n同樣今次古天樂拎最喜愛男歌手冇問題，因為的確佢人氣真係好高<br />\n同樣如果古天樂拎金銀銅我都會屌<br />\n<br />\n至於咩歌好唔好聽，努唔努力，有冇貢獻<br />\nSorry,麻煩睇清楚個獎係咩名"},{"pid":"9686b912e6646f1fdc83ec91ed8c3c32e0d465b5","tid":965382,"uid":97267,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T04:21:11.000Z","msg":"投個parttime歌手出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c90ce12ea934f8dcabe61474efb9f4fbf90cca0","tid":965382,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9686b912e6646f1fdc83ec91ed8c3c32e0d465b5","tid":965382,"uid":97267,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T04:21:11.000Z","msg":"投個parttime歌手出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T04:24:15.000Z","msg":"咁事實證明parttime都受歡迎過班fulltime<br />\n要屌都係屌班fulltime唔夠fans投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6580fd81a801b9b0191b389f334a8208d40372be","tid":965382,"uid":97267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c90ce12ea934f8dcabe61474efb9f4fbf90cca0","tid":965382,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9686b912e6646f1fdc83ec91ed8c3c32e0d465b5","tid":965382,"uid":97267,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T04:21:11.000Z","msg":"投個parttime歌手出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T04:24:15.000Z","msg":"咁事實證明parttime都受歡迎過班fulltime<br />\n要屌都係屌班fulltime唔夠fans投票<img src